{"tid":1052909,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"sony 相機真係好撚垃圾","createTime":"2019-03-08T15:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T10:49:13.000Z","uid":191921,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e629bb2cbdaa57d73668ed0d2bb746dff5bce7b6","tid":1052909,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"我指手機，原來內閧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSony 的相機及鏡頭質素早已換來大批粉絲支持，但智能手機 Xperia 的拍攝功能卻不被看重，例如在評測網站 DxOMark 的總排行榜只得 83 分，排第 19 名，輸給華為、Samsung、小米、Apple、Google 等多個競爭品牌。既然 Sony 的相機鏡頭有一定質素，為何手機攝影系統卻相差這麼遠呢？近日 Sony 全球營銷高級經理 Adam Marsh 接受 Trusted Reviews 訪問時，就解答了以上疑問：造成兩者質素分別的原因是公司內部競爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdam Marsh 表示，雖然同事們都在同一間公司內工作，但合作時也會出現障礙，例如負責 Alpha 系列的相機部門不願向負責 Xperia  系列的手機部門提供技術，不想一台小小手機也做到原本相機才有的功能。"},{"pid":"d966d97b83747c0807b4027ea15342fc39adfb60","tid":1052909,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c3b1e66df67ba6c7b8c2e9ce93f9c159d232333","tid":1052909,"uid":71341,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"789b2efe7fddb92576678d9780120ec6f82cfd82","tid":1052909,"uid":207706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d966d97b83747c0807b4027ea15342fc39adfb60","tid":1052909,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"影閃卡一流添   開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68254666cd8b75f0794dddfaddb157b73f7fea3e","tid":1052909,"uid":36157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人係最中意用富士或者用手機影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n証明女性唔喜歡執相<br />\n富士唔洗執就ok<br />\n<br /